text: King Leishemba Sanajaoba is the present king of the Manipur state of India. He is a politician of the Bharatiya Janata Party from Manipur. In the year 2020, he was elected as the Member of Rajya Sabha (Upper House) from Manipur state. == References == Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Meitei people Category:Members of the Rajya Sabha
title: Leishemba Sanajaoba
